Revision history for Term-Clui

1.75 2018-10-01 21:04:18 -0400
  - Misc administrative fixes (gh#4, gh#5 manwar++)
  - This release is functionally identical to 1.74_01.

1.74_01 2018-07-08 13:15:59 -0400
  - Remove Term::ReadKey and Term::ReadLine::Gnu as prereqs,
    these should have been optional

1.73 2018-07-08 13:06:33 -0400
  - Fixed bug where uparrow on the last choice of a
    2x2 choice of 30 chars each goes up left instead
    of up.

1.72 2018-06-25 16:20:10 -0400
  - New maintainer: PLICEASE
  - New github repository (see META.json)
  - Fix metadata typo for ExtUtils::MakeMaker (rt#120160)

